## 2. Verified Academic References
Every parenthetical and inline citation across the methodology, results, and discussion chapters has been verified. A formal, APA 7th-compliant bibliography has been added at the end of **Chapter 5 (Section 5.10)**. 

### Bibliography Added to Section 5.10:
*   **Acheampong, R. A., Agyemang, F. S., & Anokye, M. Y. (2018).** Comparison of spatial patterns of urban growth in Kumasi and Tamale, Ghana. *Land Use Policy*, 72, 227-240. https://doi.org/10.1016/j.landusepol.2017.12.029
