## 3. Formatting and Cleaning Standards Enforced
*   **Automatic Black Headings**: All headings and subheadings are styled as native Word outlines (collapsible) in Times New Roman (bold, black).
*   **Zero Em/En Dashes**: All em-dashes (`—`) and en-dashes (`–`) have been replaced with hyphens or spaces to ensure professional academic formatting compatibility.
